WHAT IS AND IS NOT PROTECTED

Protected under this license (original creative expression):
  • The "Kursi" brand, name, and identity
  • All Hinglish voice lines, sarkari persona dialogue, and in-game text
  • Role names: Neta, Bhai, Babu, Jugaadu, Vakil (and associated concepts)
  • The "License Raj Deco" visual identity (teak/brass/cream palette, rubber-stamp
    motifs, Rozha One typography, wax-seal composables, Canvas intaglio glyphs)
  • India corporate-political-underworld satire narrative and DARBAR system
  • AI persona designs (Bade Bhai, Sarkari Babu, Jungle Jugaadu, Neta Ji, …)
  • All source code, architecture, and design documents in this repository

NOT protected (public domain / uncopyrightable game mechanics):
  • The social-deduction bluffing mechanic of claiming a role and challenging
  • The underlying game-logic flow of Coup (Indie Boards and Cards)
  • General action types: income, foreign aid, tax, steal, assassinate, coup

See NOTICE for full attribution to Coup and third-party dependencies.
